prompts.prompt: I need to start a project which will be my personal webpage

I need a personal webpage with the following pages:

1. Homepage: This page should display an overview of the other pages and my GitHub stats.
2. Experience page: This page will list all of my work experiences. It should include a form to add new experiences.
3. Education page: A page to list my educational background.
4. Projects page: This page should list my projects with links to GitHub and a feature to add new projects.
